8) Rewrite of all firewall rules to improve security and reduce load on new firewall appliances;
9) Implementation of automatic penetration testing;
10) Rebuild of the Atlassian DevTools stack within AWS - latest version (currently on latest in branch) and improved scaling/resilience;
11) Liferay (6.2) Upgrade completion;
12) OpenAM Upgrade completion.

This contract has been awarded in alignment with the Crown Commercial Services RM1557.11 G Cloud 11 framework

